# 🍪 COOKIE Web Page

A modern, responsive web page showcasing delicious types of cookies.

---

## 📖 Project Overview

The site includes:

### 🟤 Hero Section
- Full viewport section
- Blurred **COOKIE** heading
- 3D cookie image for visual impact

### 🍪 Our Cookies Section
- Smooth scroll reveals a horizontal **carousel** of cookie cards  
- Cards are centered and include cookie images & names

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- **HTML5** & **CSS3** (Flexbox, Grid)
- **Google Fonts** (Bebas Neue)
- **Responsive Design** across all devices
- **Subtle Animations** (bounce effects, smooth scroll)

---

## ✨ Key Features

- 🖥️ Fullscreen hero layout with bold visuals  
- 🍪 Horizontal, scroll-activated cookie card section  
- 🎨 Warm & clean cookie-themed color palette  
- 📱 Fully responsive with smooth UX interactions  

---